items.sentence: I wonder whether Tom knows that Mary did that.
Tom had nothing to do with Mary getting fired.
Tom cleared the table and Mary did the dishes.
Tom asked Mary what she was planning on doing.
Tom and Mary dated each other for a long time.
How long has it been since you've gone skiing?
I knew that something bad was about to happen.
You went to the beach last Monday, didn't you?
Tom is at the door. Please ask him to come in.
It seems that Tom's only choice is to do that.
